commandDescription: Command to extract all test classes from commits messages from GIT differences between branches, commits or tags
sourceFlagDescription: Source branch, commit, tag... to extract test classes from commit messages
targetFlagDescription: Target branch, commit, tag... to extract test classes from commit messages
startTagFlagDescription: Start Tag for Test Classes names on git commit message. (default: --TESTS START--)
endTagFlagDescription: End Tag for Test Classes names on git commit message (default: --TESTS END--)
runningExtractTestClassesMessage: Extracting Test Classes from git commits messages...
examples: sfdx ah:git:test:extract -s branchX -t main --starttag "MyCustom Test Start Tag" --endtag "MyCustom Test End Tag" --json
